    day: 20, week: 3, title: 'Chakra Awakening: The Full Energy Column', theme: 'Complete Chakra Activation', duration: '45 minutes',
    teaching: "The third eye does not operate in isolation. It is one point in a complete system of energy centres running from the base of the spine to the crown of the head. When the entire system is balanced and flowing, the inner eye receives clear, unobstructed information. When lower centres are blocked, the third eye\u2019s signal is distorted.\n\nThink of it as a radio tower. The Ajna is the transmitter and receiver. But if the foundation is unstable or the wiring is damaged, even the most powerful transmitter produces static. Working with the full chakra system is essential, not optional.\n\nThe seven centres:\n\nROOT (Muladhara) \u2014 Base of spine. Governs safety, survival, physical groundedness, belonging. Colour: deep red. Element: earth. When blocked: chronic anxiety, financial fear, inability to be present.\n\nSACRAL (Svadhisthana) \u2014 Below navel. Governs creativity, sexuality, emotional fluidity, pleasure. Colour: warm orange. Element: water. When blocked: creative blocks, emotional numbness, difficulty with intimacy.\n\nSOLAR PLEXUS (Manipura) \u2014 Above navel. Governs personal power, self-worth, will, confidence. Colour: bright yellow. Element: fire. When blocked: people-pleasing, inability to set boundaries, chronic self-doubt.\n\nHEART (Anahata) \u2014 Centre of chest. Governs love, compassion, connection, forgiveness. Colour: emerald green. Element: air. When blocked: inability to give or receive love, unresolved grief, isolation.\n\nTHROAT (Vishuddha) \u2014 Centre of throat. Governs expression, truth, communication, authenticity. Colour: bright blue. Element: sound. When blocked: difficulty speaking truth, fear of being seen.\n\nTHIRD EYE (Ajna) \u2014 Centre of forehead. Governs intuition, inner vision, wisdom, discernment. Colour: deep indigo. Element: light. When blocked: mental fog, rigid thinking.\n\nCROWN (Sahasrara) \u2014 Top of head. Governs spiritual connection, cosmic awareness, divine presence. Colour: violet or white. Element: consciousness. When blocked: spiritual disconnection, existential emptiness.",
    practice: "The Full Chakra Activation Meditation (45 minutes):\n\nLie down comfortably on your back. Close your eyes. Take 10 slow, deep breaths until your body is completely relaxed.\n\nYou will move through each chakra from base upward, spending 4\u20135 minutes at each centre.\n\nROOT: Bring awareness to the base of your spine. Visualise a deep red sphere, warm and dense as the earth. Breathe into it. Feel your connection to the physical world, to the ground, to the safety of your body.\n\nSACRAL: Move below the navel. See warm orange light, fluid and creative. Breathe into your creative centre. Release any shame about pleasure or desire.\n\nSOLAR PLEXUS: Above the navel. Visualise a bright yellow sun at your centre. Feel your personal power, your right to take up space. Let this light burn through self-doubt.\n\nHEART: Centre of chest. See luminous emerald green radiating in all directions. Allow your heart to open like a flower turning toward the sun. Breathe love in. Breathe love out. Stay as long as you need.\n\nTHROAT: Centre of throat. See clear bright blue light. Feel the truth that lives in you that has not yet been spoken. Give it permission to exist.\n\nTHIRD EYE: Centre of forehead. The deep indigo flame. Allow it to glow and pulse. You are home. Rest here for a full 5 minutes.\n\nCROWN: Top of head. See violet or pure white light opening like a lotus. Feel the connection to something vast above you. Allow the boundary between yourself and larger consciousness to become permeable.\n\nINTEGRATION: Visualise a column of light running from crown through all seven centres to the base, and from there into the earth. All centres aligned. All centres glowing. Rest here for 5 minutes in complete stillness.",
    journalPrompt: "Which chakra felt most blocked or resistant during today\u2019s practice? What domain of life does that centre govern? What does this tell you about where your growth edge currently is? Which chakra felt most alive and open?",
